 110:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_uart_ex.c ****         (++) TX and/or RX pin level inversion
 111:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_uart_ex.c ****         (++) data logical level inversion
