 115:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_uart_ex.c ****         (++) MSB first on communication line
 116:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_uart_ex.c ****         (++) auto Baud rate detection
